# Breadcrumb

`TxBreadcrumb` renders a semantic breadcrumb trail for hierarchical navigation. Items can be native links, manual click targets, disabled entries, or the current page.

Reviewed against `packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/breadcrumb/src/types.ts`, `TxBreadcrumb.vue`, and `breadcrumb.test.ts`.

## Basic Usage

::::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="BreadcrumbBreadcrumbTrailDemo" code-lang="vue"}
